videos.description: Washington State forward Drick Bernstine backs down his defender and dishes a sweet no-look wraparound pass to Malachi Flynn for the basket.
videos.headline: Cougars' Bernstine drops no-look dime

videos.description: Cougars guard Malachi Flynn shows off his shooting range, sinking his 3-pointer from well beyond the arc with a defender in his face.
videos.headline: Washington State's Flynn drills deep triple

videos.description: Victor Bailey Jr. gets the ball in transition and winds up for a big one-handed jam, but misses and teammate Kenny Wooten cleans up with a slam.
videos.headline: Oregon's Bailey Jr. blows wide-open dunk

videos.description: Washington State head coach Ernie Kent says his team was able to hold Oregon to just 17 first-half points by constantly changing defensive schemes.
videos.headline: Kent thrilled with Cougars' 1st-half defense

videos.description: Washington State's Drick Bernstine continues to show off his passing skills, splitting two defenders to hit Carter Skaggs in stride for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Bernstine dishes sweet bounce pass for Cougars score

videos.description: Oregon's MiKyle McIntosh misses his jump shot, but Paul White is there to grab the offensive board and put it back in, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Oregon's White cleans up on offensive glass

videos.description: Oregon's Payton Pritchard gets the ball in the corner and knocks down his fourth 3-pointer of the night to cut Washington State's lead to just one.
videos.headline: Ducks' Pritchard drains corner 3

videos.description: Ducks guard Troy Brown picks Drick Bernstine's pocket and finishes in transition with a thunderous one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Oregon's Brown steals and slams

videos.description: Trailing by three with under a minute to go, Cougars guard Malachi Flynn connects from deep to tie the game at 53 and send it to overtime.
videos.headline: Flynn's clutch triple ties it up for Washington State

videos.description: Washington State guard Malachi Flynn sizes up his man off the dribble and connects with a deep triple to put the Cougars ahead 57-55.
videos.headline: Cougars' Flynn sinks go-ahead 3 in OT

videos.description: Trailing by one with under 30 seconds to play in overtime, Ducks guard Payton Pritchard drives and gets his floater to drop to put Oregon ahead 63-62.
videos.headline: Pritchard's clutch floater gives Oregon the lead
